The paper discusses the security challenges in building automation systems and proposes techniques to analyze and visualize data to aid in building security decision making. This falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The techniques involve data analysis and visualization, which can be related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and social and information networks (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the complexity of modern-day systems, which can be related to software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper discusses the security issues in building automation systems, which can be related to cybersecurity (cs.CY).
